seo_en: spark api unauth vulnerability, unauthorized access, security detection
summary: 该插件用于检测Spark API是否存在未授权访问漏洞，通过发送请求检查特定端点的响应来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether there is an unauthorized access vulnerability in the Spark API, confirming the existence of the vulnerability by checking the response of specific endpoints.
